data.description: Excellent Investment Opportunity*  Introducing this stunning two bedroom updated ranch home with luxury vinyl floors that grace the entire main floor, offering both elegance and durability. This recently updated property boasts a brand-new water heater, refrigerator, microwave, range and backsplash. The bathroom features a modern walk-in shower and new toilet fixtures providing convenience and style. With its spacious bedrooms, this home offers comfort and versatility, making perfect for those seeking a cozy retreat. Don't miss the opportunity to call this beautifully appointed residence your new home sweet home.
